// Test: freeing an already-freed sprite id is a runtime error (unlike
// widgets, which treat stale ids as silent no-ops — sprites are a
// lower-level resource and a double-free is a script bug).
var s = createSprite(2, 2, "XXXX");
freeSprite(s);
freeSprite(s);
// expect runtime error: freeSprite() sprite already freed.
